data.description: Simply Stunning! This Italianate Victorian Style Fortress reeks of character & craftsmanship. The air of class and elegance from the woodwork & hardwoods engulfs the senses. 2600 sq ft is ample space for most & the 4 bedrooms are spacious. Three fireplaces add appeal and warmth. The rear family room exits to a composite deck--the SunSetter awning will keep you cool! The fenced yard is peaceful & private. Large 3 car detached garage. New AC unit, with 10 year warranty installed September 2018. The basement was completely dugout and poured in 2005 w/ new block foundation. Close to maintenance free- over $75K of documented improvements.
data.whatILove: Loads of character! There is something special about an older home! The basement was completely re-poured a few years ago and now has 9 foot ceilings...the basement could be finished into a killer man cave! The winding staircase is stunning...just stunning! Two fireplaces, a parlor, a formal dining room, and a rear family room are icing on the cake. This home is hard to beat. The front porch is inviting and open and the rear deck is covered by a SunSetter awning. The deck flows into a large fenced back yard. Wow!!
